Installation of the Docker Indicator
============================================


Installation from package
-------------------------

You should always prefer the standard package distribution mechanism (PPA). To
install the application from my PPA:

  1. Add the PPA:

    sudo apt-add-repository ppa:yktooo/ppa

  2. Update the package list:

    sudo apt-get update

  3. Install the package:

    sudo apt-get install indicator-docker


Installation from the source tarball
------------------------------------

In order to install the application from the source tarball:

  1. Download the tarball (indicator-docker-*.tar.gz)

  2. Decompress the archive

  3. cd to the indicator-docker-* dir

  4. Run:

    sudo python3 setup.py install
